<p>There's something about this time of year that always makes me wistful for the good old daysâ€”the simpler times, if you willâ€”when all that mattered were family, friends, and a whole lotta blogging about everything under the sun. I miss those days, don't you?</p>
<p>Fear not, my fellow blogging friends. We've got you all covered today with a theme that will make you want to stop time and write about everything in your lives until you can't write anymore.</p>
<p>A Simpler Time, designed by <a title="Denise Chandler" href="http://www.denisechandler.com/" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">Denise Chandler</a>, is a theme that's beautiful, bold, and memorableâ€”pretty much exactly like the types of stories you'll be writing alongside it on your WordPress.com blog:</p>
